        {
            "title": "為何應該趁谷歌消息引發的記憶體股回調買入",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Q6h6QwxW6sSH1MqrHXbmsg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA6U04V_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 記憶體股週三下跌,投資者對谷歌宣布推出TurboQuant做出反應,這是一種旨在減少AI系統記憶體需求的新壓縮演算法,儘管科技板塊整體錄得上漲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">SanDisk Corporation (NASDAQ:SNDK)下跌5%,美光科技(NASDAQ:MU)下跌4%,西部數據(NASDAQ:WDC)下跌3.7%,希捷科技(NASDAQ:STX)下跌4%。這些跌幅發生在納斯達克100指數上漲之際。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-4fd5e88f-17ee-3178-9e73-f0050d821644-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">谷歌的TurboQuant對AI模型使用3位元壓縮技術。然而,Lynx Equity Strategies分析師KC <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Rajkumar\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:Rajkumar;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Rajkumar\">Rajkumar</a>在給客戶的報告中質疑這一發展的重要性。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">\"向量量化並非新概念,因為大型語言模型已經從原始訓練模型的32位元數據發展到今天推理模型使用的4位元數據,\"Rajkumar寫道。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該分析師對第三方科技博客對該技術的描述提出異議,稱其報導過度誇大。Rajkumar反駁了8倍改進的說法,指出這一比較是與較舊的32位元模型進行的,而非目前使用的4位元量化模型。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">\"雖然可能有所改進,但我們認為並非8倍,\"Rajkumar表示。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該分析師指出,隨著推理中的標記上下文長度增加,AI供應商需要創新以解決瓶頸問題。然而,Rajkumar表示,由於供應限制,這並不會減少未來三到五年對記憶體和快閃記憶體的需求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">\"先進的壓縮技術僅能減少瓶頸,而不會摧毀對動態隨機存取記憶體/快閃記憶體的需求,\"Rajkumar寫道。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Lynx Equity Strategies維持對<span><span>美光科技</span></span>700美元的目標價,並重申其買入建議。\"我們會在今日谷歌相關的回調中買入,\"該分析師補充道。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
