        {
            "title": "MU、WDC、SNDK下跌:為何Google的TurboQuant令記憶體股震盪",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/9JNZKY6n10_bBMBp286eBQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEB7R05V_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 儘管科技板塊整體表現強勁,記憶體股週三仍然下跌。在Google推出TurboQuant這項可能降低AI系統記憶體需求的新壓縮演算法後,相關股價應聲下挫。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">SanDisk Corporation(NASDAQ:SNDK)下跌5.7%,美光科技(NASDAQ:MU)下跌3%,西部數據(NASDAQ:WDC)下跌4.7%,希捷科技(NASDAQ:STX)下跌4%。這些跌幅出現在納斯達克100指數上漲之際。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-4bbafae1-a94f-3256-9e9b-ea8286815675-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Google推出了TurboQuant,這是一項旨在降低大型語言模型和向量搜尋引擎記憶體消耗的壓縮技術。該演算法解決了鍵值快取的瓶頸問題,鍵值快取用於儲存AI系統中經常存取的資訊。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據Google的公告,TurboQuant可以將鍵值快取壓縮至3位元,無需訓練或微調,同時保持模型準確性。在包括Gemma和Mistral在內的開源模型上進行的測試顯示,該技術實現了鍵值記憶體大小6倍的縮減。該演算法還在H100 GPU加速器上展現了比未量化鍵值高達8倍的效能提升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該技術透過兩個步驟運作:應用PolarQuant方法透過旋轉資料向量實現高品質壓縮,以及使用量化Johnson-Lindenstrauss演算法消除殘餘誤差。Google表示,傳統的向量量化方法在記憶體開銷中每個數字增加1至2個額外位元,部分抵消了壓縮優勢。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">TurboQuant將在ICLR 2026上發表,而PolarQuant計劃在AISTATS 2026上發表。Google在包括LongBench、Needle In A Haystack、ZeroSCROLLS、RULER和L-Eval在內的基準測試中測試了這些演算法。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該技術的應用範圍超越了AI模型,還包括為大規模搜尋引擎提供動力的向量搜尋功能。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">記憶體股今年迄今已大幅上漲,使其容易受到可能降低需求的發展影響。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/mu-wdc-sndk%E4%B8%8B%E8%B7%8C-%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95google%E7%9A%84turboquant%E4%BB%A4%E8%A8%98%E6%86%B6%E9%AB%94%E8%82%A1%E9%9C%87%E7%9B%AA-144945449.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-25 23:11:54",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "亞馬遜股價:Wolfe量化燃料成本上漲的影響",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Linaol8dBpjX_6D2P1VUNg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA6H0CU_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 亞馬遜(Amazon)面臨燃料成本上升帶來的短期盈利壓力,Wolfe Research下調了其營業收入(OI)預測,但仍維持對該股的正面看法。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該券商表示,由於燃料成本上升,將2026財年(FY26)營業收入預估下調低個位數百分比(LSD)。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分析師Shweta Khajuria在報告中指出:「具體而言,我們預計第一季將面臨2個百分點的阻力,第二季則面臨中個位數百分比(MSD%)的阻力。」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-5dbbf5a4-6a53-37ca-a005-a7ee75009b84-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此次預測調整源於柴油價格的急劇上漲,目前已攀升至每加侖5美元以上,較美國與伊朗衝突前的水平上漲超過30%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">鑑於亞馬遜擁有大規模的物流網絡,Khajuria預計成本將受到重大影響。她估計燃料約佔運輸費用的15%,並預測若燃料價格在整個季度維持高位,第一季燃料通膨將達12%,第二季則達35%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該分析師指出:「這意味著第一季和第二季將分別增加約4億美元和12億美元的燃料成本。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">但她表示,即使主要下調了上半年的預估,Wolfe「在營業收入方面仍比市場預期高4.4%,在營收方面高1.0%。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Khajuria還提到定價可能帶來的抵消效果。她表示,燃料阻力「可能通過將美國Prime會員價格提高20美元而大幅抵消。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該分析師寫道:「我們估計美國有8500萬個Prime會員家庭,若Prime價格上調20美元,可能帶來17億美元的高利潤率增量收入。我們尚未將此納入預估中。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在政策層面,她指出川普政府正考慮每日從儲備中釋放100萬至150萬桶石油,這可能有助於緩解柴油價格並限制成本影響。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Wolfe維持亞馬遜「跑贏大盤」(Outperform)評級,目標價從250美元下調至245美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
